## SUMMARY FOR DEVS

### Tutorial Requirements

- 5 chapters, 1 minute each
- No reading required (voice/visuals only)
- Player clicks everything themselves
- Victory at the end
- Rewards after completion
- Replayable tutorial (with skip option for alts)

### Must-Have Elements

- Green glow = click this
- Satisfying sounds for correct actions
- Confetti for victories (even small ones)
- Encouraging narrator (never condescending)
- Visual layer shifts that feel POWERFUL

